#: app/templates/landing.html:558
msgid "Coordinate field campaigns"
msgstr "I-coordinate ang mga field campaign"

#: app/templates/landing.html:561
msgid ""
"Enhancing field mapping efficiency and accuracy through seamless "
"coordination."
msgstr ""
"Pinapahusay ang kahusayan at katumpakan ng field mapping sa pamamagitan "
"ng maayos na koordinasyon."

#: app/templates/landing.html:565
msgid "Explore Projects"
msgstr "Tuklasin ang mga Proyekto"

#: app/templates/landing.html:578
msgid "Loading metrics..."
msgstr "Nilo-load ang mga sukatan..."

#: app/templates/landing.html:586
msgid "What is it?"
msgstr "Ano ito?"

#: app/templates/landing.html:588
msgid ""
"The Field Tasking Manager (Field-TM) helps teams add local knowledge to "
"map features\n"
"        by coordinating mapping in the field."
msgstr ""
"Tinutulungan ng Field Tasking Manager (Field-TM) ang mga team na "
"magdagdag ng lokal na kaalaman sa mga feature ng mapa sa pamamagitan ng "
"pag-coordinate ng field mapping."

#: app/templates/landing.html:592
msgid ""
"Field-TM facilitates collaborative mapping by supporting and extending "
"mature tools\n"
"        like ODK and QField. It is a standalone mobile and web workflow "
"that helps teams collect\n"
"        geospatial data efficiently with commonly available Android "
"devices."
msgstr ""
"Pinapadali ng Field-TM ang collaborative mapping sa pamamagitan ng "
"pagsuporta at pagpapalawak sa mga matatag nang tool gaya ng ODK at "
"QField. Isa itong standalone na mobile at web workflow na tumutulong sa "
"mga team na mahusay na mangolekta ng geospatial data gamit ang karaniwang"
" available na mga Android device."

#: app/templates/landing.html:599
msgid "A project manager demonstrates FieldTM mapping workflow on a laptop"
msgstr ""
"Isang project manager ang nagpapakita ng FieldTM mapping workflow sa "
"isang laptop"

#: app/templates/landing.html:605
msgid "Main Features"
msgstr "Pangunahing Mga Tampok"

#: app/templates/landing.html:608
msgid "Flexible Data Collection"
msgstr "Nababagong Pagkolekta ng Data"

#: app/templates/landing.html:610
msgid ""
"Support diverse survey forms, multiple data formats, and adaptable "
"workflows that\n"
"          fit different operational needs."
msgstr ""
"Sinusuportahan ang iba't ibang survey form, maraming format ng data, at "
"nababagong workflow na akma sa iba't ibang pangangailangan sa operasyon."

#: app/templates/landing.html:615
msgid "Open Source and Customizable"
msgstr "Open Source at Nako-customize"

#: app/templates/landing.html:617
msgid ""
"Adapt Field-TM to your own survey logic, data structures, and integration"
"\n"
"          requirements."
msgstr ""
"Iangkop ang Field-TM sa sarili mong survey logic, mga istruktura ng data,"
" at mga pangangailangan sa integration."

#: app/templates/landing.html:622
msgid "Entity-Level Tracking"
msgstr "Pagsubaybay sa Antas ng Entity"

#: app/templates/landing.html:624
msgid ""
"Monitor survey progress at task and feature level so managers can make "
"informed\n"
"          decisions quickly."
msgstr ""
"Subaybayan ang progreso ng survey sa antas ng gawain at feature upang "
"mabilis na makagawa ng desisyong may sapat na basehan ang mga manager."

#: app/templates/landing.html:632
msgid "Who is it for?"
msgstr "Para kanino ito?"

#: app/templates/landing.html:635
msgid "Project Manager"
msgstr "Tagapamahala ng Proyekto"

#: app/templates/landing.html:636
msgid "Create and coordinate field campaigns"
msgstr "Lumikha at mag-coordinate ng mga field campaign"

#: app/templates/landing.html:638
msgid ""
"Project managers use Field-TM to set up mapping projects, define areas of"
" interest,\n"
"          design survey forms, and split work into manageable tasks."
msgstr ""
"Ginagamit ng mga project manager ang Field-TM upang mag-set up ng mga "
"mapping project, tukuyin ang mga area of interest, magdisenyo ng mga "
"survey form, at hatiin ang trabaho sa mga gawaing madaling pamahalaan."

#: app/templates/landing.html:642
msgid "Define a project area and upload or choose a survey form"
msgstr "Tukuyin ang lugar ng proyekto at mag-upload o pumili ng survey form"

#: app/templates/landing.html:643
msgid "Split the area into tasks and generate a data extract"
msgstr "Hatiin ang lugar sa mga gawain at bumuo ng data extract"

#: app/templates/landing.html:644
msgid "Publish the project to ODK Central or QFieldCloud"
msgstr "I-publish ang proyekto sa ODK Central o QFieldCloud"

#: app/templates/landing.html:645
msgid "Share a QR code so mappers can start collecting data"
msgstr ""
"Magbahagi ng QR code upang makapagsimulang mangolekta ng data ang mga "
"mapper"

#: app/templates/landing.html:649
msgid "Field Mapper"
msgstr "Tagapagmapa sa Field"

#: app/templates/landing.html:650
msgid "Collect data in the field with your phone"
msgstr "Mangolekta ng data sa field gamit ang iyong telepono"

#: app/templates/landing.html:652
msgid ""
"Mappers do not need to log in to Field-TM. Once a project manager "
"publishes a\n"
"          project, mappers access it directly in their mobile app of "
"choice."
msgstr ""
"Hindi kailangang mag-log in ng mga mapper sa Field-TM. Kapag na-publish "
"na ng project manager ang isang proyekto, direkta nila itong maa-access "
"sa mobile app na kanilang pinili."

#: app/templates/landing.html:656
msgid "Scan the QR code shared by your project manager"
msgstr "I-scan ang QR code na ibinahagi ng iyong project manager"

#: app/templates/landing.html:657
msgid "The project loads automatically in ODK Collect or QField"
msgstr "Awtomatikong nilo-load ang proyekto sa ODK Collect o QField"

#: app/templates/landing.html:658
msgid "Navigate to your assigned task area and collect data"
msgstr "Pumunta sa nakatalagang task area at mangolekta ng data"

#: app/templates/landing.html:659
msgid "Submit your survey, which goes straight to the server"
msgstr "Isumite ang iyong survey, na direktang mapupunta sa server"

#: app/templates/landing.html:666
msgid "Field-TM Use Cases"
msgstr "Mga Use Case ng Field-TM"

#: app/templates/landing.html:671
msgid "Field mapping in progress"
msgstr "Isinasagawang field mapping"

#: app/templates/landing.html:676
msgid "1. Community Mapping"
msgstr "1. Pagmamapa ng Komunidad"

#: app/templates/landing.html:678
msgid ""
"Field Tasking Manager empowers communities to map informal settlements, "
"public\n"
"            facilities, and local services for inclusive planning."
msgstr ""
"Binibigyang-kakayahan ng Field Tasking Manager ang mga komunidad na i-map"
" ang mga impormal na pamayanan, pampublikong pasilidad, at lokal na "
"serbisyo para sa inklusibong pagpaplano."

#: app/templates/landing.html:683
msgid "2. Urban Planning and Management"
msgstr "2. Urban Planning at Pamamahala"

#: app/templates/landing.html:685
msgid ""
"Build smarter cities with coordinated surveys of houses, roads, and "
"utilities\n"
"            through clear, manageable mapping tasks."
msgstr ""
"Bumuo ng mas matatalinong lungsod sa pamamagitan ng magkakaugnay na "
"survey ng mga bahay, kalsada, at utility gamit ang malinaw at madaling "
"pamahalaang mga gawaing pang-mapping."

#: app/templates/landing.html:690
msgid "3. Disaster Response and Recovery"
msgstr "3. Pagtugon at Pagbangon mula sa Sakuna"

#: app/templates/landing.html:692
msgid ""
"Rapidly map damaged infrastructure after disasters, coordinate "
"volunteers, and\n"
"            deliver reliable data for relief operations."
msgstr ""
"Mabilis na i-map ang mga nasirang imprastraktura pagkatapos ng sakuna, "
"i-coordinate ang mga boluntaryo, at maghatid ng mapagkakatiwalaang data "
"para sa mga operasyong pangtulong."

#: app/templates/landing.html:701
msgid "Resources"
msgstr "Mga Resource"

#: app/templates/landing.html:709
msgid "Data Prep"
msgstr "Paghahanda ng Data"

#: app/templates/landing.html:710
msgid "HOT Export Tool"
